{"tid":1243853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果621唔夠人，民間運動將會柒到不堪","createTime":"2019-06-19T15:42:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T03:08:17.000Z","uid":31215,"like":69,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cc0c2e2b655e5dff1a24e5b0b0c20d716ecbd1b3","tid":1243853,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:42:01.000Z","msg":"自古以黎<br />\n大型民主運動<br />\n主要都係由傳統泛民同民陣牽頭搞<br />\n今次大台唔號召，蘋果唔再宣傳<br />\n最主力宣傳單位係連登<br />\n如果搞左咁多野<br />\n人數同撐送中撐警察大遊行差唔多咁少<br />\n連登將會名譽掃地，同時民陣會沾沾自喜，心諗冇佢真係唔成事<br />\n唔係要分化<br />\n但今次係一個好機會<br />\n俾全世界睇到冇大台靠網上號召都可以一呼百應<br />\n連登仔唔好俾人睇死<br />\n放低你嘅鍵盤<br />\n唔衝都出黎睇下食下花生<br />\n<br />\n連登係龍定蛇就睇今次<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">到時見！</span>"},{"pid":"5b2df41669e2f7ae08c6a0271c6a57e17fe1c4e5","tid":1243853,"uid":129310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2106133c9e08bcf1f61da43e5d1f3ca3b415aef7","tid":1243853,"uid":103347,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:45:49.000Z","msg":"連續遊兩個星期勒...大家都累<br />\n少人d都可以理解 又出黎行完就散 有咩意思..."},{"pid":"a278007c3f2db97edd67af46a9bf7e3d086bfc72","tid":1243853,"uid":143667,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:46:39.000Z","msg":"sor 多口問句，點解會揀21號？星期六唔係仲多人咩？<br />\n真心唔知，勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac89a8b0019db877b66166ccd78631ccc362e9ec","tid":1243853,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:46:43.000Z","msg":"到時夢中相見"},{"pid":"2820025b32413adf6f118df10cc825ee42654cc3","tid":1243853,"uid":104086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:47:23.000Z","msg":"推推推推推推！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"2af3f0bcf728062d248beea95a752ebc9ec7fcac","tid":1243853,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2106133c9e08bcf1f61da43e5d1f3ca3b415aef7","tid":1243853,"uid":103347,"l